Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that is in my world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:43.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,is smell, sound, taste and touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:46.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:49.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:02.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's something in my eye.
