Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.95,0:02:26.91,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1300,0)\be1}Eye of Fortune, Eye of Misfortune
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:36.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm finally in a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:54.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the ceiling hangs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:03:02.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like hair, a black strand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:09.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At night downward it grows
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:17.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I can't sleep, it gets in my nose!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a Mushi she's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you hear that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,From my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want to hear more, Mushi-shi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you know I'm a Mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just got that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, don't look so shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's getting late. Let's find an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, I don't intend to stay the ni–
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go! Give me back my stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:21.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:25.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,what should I talk about next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is your dad a Mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All your stories seem to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he gone now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only because my eyes were of no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I can see well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:55.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw a Ganpuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw a Ganpuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn. That's a really rare Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:07.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I think I'll talk about myself next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:20.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you bury these eyes in the mountains for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amane!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're home. How was work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:42.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father, a Mushi-shi, often left me home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:48.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,More than anything, I loved listening\Nto my father's travel stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:53.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got something awesome this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:58.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a Mushi called a Ganpuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was thought to be a myth until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:07.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I got my hands on an eyeball of a guy who saw one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,An eyeball?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I took it after he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the few years after he saw the Ganpuku,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,his eyesight kept getting better and better until he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:24.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here's that eyeball, not even rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:28.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might lead us to the Ganpuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amane,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:35.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make sure you can see,\Neven if it takes me my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promise. Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:51.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:53.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wro–
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Mushi. It was in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might have been the Ganpuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:09.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad searched all over the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:16.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a month later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:26.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's something in my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what it means to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:40.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something in my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you, right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amane!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:26.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I understood what it means to "see".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:32.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could never even imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:40.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was more ecstatic than\NI could have ever dreamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:43.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dark blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:51.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are geese.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're lined up so neatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saki-chan and Fusa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come you can see now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw something that looked like a shining flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:09.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My eyes could see further than any of my friends' could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:14.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you are in the grass, You-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Peek-a-boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amane-chan, you're too good at finding us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't allowed to be {\i1}it{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:35.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,With time, I came to see things in places\Nthat couldn't have been seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hill beyond the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the mountain range beyond the hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and even the sea far beyond the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could see all of it from inside my own room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:06.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I loved watching distant scenes and people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:14.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soon I started feeling dizzy and had trouble walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:21.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time I could have peace and\Ndarkness was when I closed my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since then, I've had my eyes closed a lot of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:36.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as time passed again, I began to see new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:42.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch ou–
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wind got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:09.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I closed my eyes, I could see the\Npast and future of those around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:15.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,People began to show up asking\Nfor their futures to be told.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The visions I saw all became reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:24.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rumors spread that I was an oracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,People even gathered from neighboring towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next summer, you will fall into a river
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:39.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, don't go near any rivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:47.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even when I warned them, what\NI saw would never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:55.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then people only came to inquire\Nabout thieves and cheaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My eyes were always cherished,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but in time, I had no one I could call a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:12.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oracles are just creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even change anything I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:24.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stopped seeing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:28.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see outside through my eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amane, I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amane?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:52.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see your future and the outside both at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:11.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my father never came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:19.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Day after day, I searched for my\Nfather with my second sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:25.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:29.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found my father in the bottom of a valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I traveled to mourn for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:43.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I walked, telling my father's stories\Non my biwa to raise money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:49.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after I finally arrived at my father's remains,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:54.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't intend on returning home\Nto where my father was no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:14:00.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I continued traveling in the cities, playing my {\i1}biwa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:12.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As time passed, I could see more\Nand more through my eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing could obstruct my vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:19.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even stand straight during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:25.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was something I still couldn't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:29.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My own future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:35.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, I can see that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:42.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd have to ask this of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:46.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I foresaw all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:51.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you want me to pull out those eyes of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and throw them out in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:15:00.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would have done that myself if that was\Nall that I was going to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:05.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,These eyes brought me happiness at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:10.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I lived with them even though they're vile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:16.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But soon these eyes will not be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the Ganpuku that I saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's going to fly out of my eyeballs,\Ndig itself into the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and wait for a new set of eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:30.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to bury them deep in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:35.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that no one has to go through what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you can see all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:42.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd understand if you wanted your eyes fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't be sure there aren't any treatments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:54.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you that what I see can't be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:16:02.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What my eyes see is "fate" far beyond our grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:22.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit back and take everything you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:24.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:29.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your friend won't have anything good to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to help me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it because you lost your left eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can see it with your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:46.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't see your childhood. It's pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My oldest memories are from when I was around ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:57.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was walking in the dark, in the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:05.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I fumbled around, and soon I saw the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:12.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The phony-looking white moon\Nset, and again rose a moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I wandered through there for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:20.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally came to a place where I could see the sun rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:27.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still remember how thankful I was for that sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:33.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you afraid of losing light forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm more afraid of a world with nothing but light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:47.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you could see everything but couldn't change {\i1}any{\i0} of it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:51.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,or if you could live in freedom in darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:55.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which do you think is more fortunate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:18:04.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it might not be that bad living\Nin the dark, remembering the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:29.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just saw it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How far ahead can you see now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:37.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until the moment that these eyes die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:47.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her eyes could never see through her eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They could only see others' futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:56.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For her eyes to see her own future\Nand to see through her eyelids –
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:01.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}could it be that her eyes are\Nbecoming independent of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:05.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Mushi infects the eyes by being seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:11.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It transforms the eyes so that they\Nlive on after the body dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:16.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In time when it completely takes over, it leaves the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's the case, it's going to split off soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still no response to my letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:41.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Fate" far beyond our grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:54.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? I can't see past the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:02.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:07.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My eyes are moving on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:15.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I'll get you some pain killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:38.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you don't need eyes to shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:21:00.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far ahead can you see now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:05.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until the moment that these eyes die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:11.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My eyeballs are there buried in the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:17.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soon they arise, and an animal approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:23.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beautiful flowers appear in the animal's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:27.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And as soon as they get sucked into its eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:33.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}everything becomes black.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:40.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you should have gotten your letter by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.40,caligraph,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...research...\N...no known treatments...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going back to your hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:55.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:22:00.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to go on alone for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:04.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that I can't see the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:08.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, say hi to me if you ever see me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:13.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get better at the {\i1}biwa{\i0}.
